These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, thai, canadian, spanish, indian, italian
7 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, rabbit, lizard, frog, hamster, horse
 1. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 2. the thai is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 3. the italian is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 4. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 5. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the italian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
11. the indian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
12. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
13. the indian is in the middle##1
14. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
15. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
16. the owner of the frog is not the italian##6
17. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
18. the owner of the goldfish is not the thai##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | canadian | spanish | indian | italian | thai | dutch |
| Pet           | lizard   | hamster    | horse       | snake     | rabbit    | frog   | goldfish |

