.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, disco, techno, salsa, blues, gospel, rock
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, russian, mexican, egyptian, indonesian, italian, colombian
 1. the egyptian is not the fan disco##6
 2. the indonesian is not the fan disco##6
 3. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the fan gospel##5
 4. the fan salsa is on the left of the mexican##1
 5. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
 6. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
 7. the pakistani is on the left of the indonesian##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left or right of the fan funk##3
 9. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the fan disco##5
10. the indonesian is on the right of the fan techno##1
11. the fan techno is not the mexican##6
12. the fan funk is on the far right##1
13. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
14. the fan salsa is the italian##1
15. the indonesian is on the left of the fan salsa##1
16. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
17. the mexican is on the right of the fan salsa##1
18. the fan salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
19. the fan disco is on the right of the fan rock##1
20. the fan gospel is on the right of the fan techno##1
21. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the italian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |    5     |   6    |     7     |
