.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, chef, mechanic, police-officer, videographer, journalist, lawyer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, climbing, lacrosse, basketball, golf, sailing
 1. the chef is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 4. the designer is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
 6. the videographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 7. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
10. the person who's sport is sailing is not the journalist##6
11. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
12. the designer is in an even position##4
13. the person who's sport is rowing is not the lawyer##6
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is rowing and the mechanic##2
15. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
16. the designer is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |      3       |    4    |       5       |         6          |      7      |
| Job     | mechanic | lawyer      | videographer | designer  | police-officer      | journalist | chef |
| Sport   | golf       | lacrosse | rowing      | basketball | sailing | climbing      | volleyball    |

