.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-5::.
There 7 different types of food: cabbage, pomegranate, mango, watermelon, pepper, carrot, orange
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, tram, train, car, roller, bus
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
 3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 5. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
 6. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
 7. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
11. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
13. the person driving the bike is not the person eating pomegranate##6
14. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
15. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
16. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
18. the person eating carrot is not the person driving the tram##6
19. the person eating carrot is between the person eating pepper and the person driving the train##2
20. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |    4    |   5    |     6     |     7      |
| Food        | pepper | carrot     | pomegranate | orange | cabbage | watermelon    | mango   |
| Transport   | bus      | bike | train  | quad-bike    | roller | tram | car |

