The people use 7 different means of transport: car, skateboard, ship, trike, jet-ski, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person driving the trike##6
 5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 6. the owner of the horse is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 7. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not the person driving the ship##6
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
11. the owner of the pony is the person driving the taxi##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
14. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
15. the owner of the goldfish is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
16. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

