.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up, juice, coffee
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, western, musical, fantasy, romance, documentary, adventure
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 4. the person drinking juice is not the person watching western movies##6
 5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking sprite and the person watching western movies##2
12. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
14. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
15. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
16. the person watching adventure movies is not the person drinking coffee##6
17. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching spy movies##1
18. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
